  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients with type 1 diabetes

          -  Age &gt;18 years

          -  Diabetes duration more than 12 months

          -  Multiple Daily Injections therapy (fast acting analog for meals; long acting analog as
             basal)

          -  HbA1c between 8.0% and 11.3%

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Present or former practice of carbohydrate counting

          -  Gastroparesis

          -  Pregnancy or nursing
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
